{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SoV2GK8jwkpby3DKr7EW1Y","type":"tool_result","content":"   400→- Any incomplete work that creates blocking dependencies?\n   401→\n   402→<action>Note potential gaps or preparation needed:</action>\n   403→\n   404→- Technical setup required (infrastructure, tools, libraries)\n   405→- Knowledge gaps to fill (research, training, spikes)\n   406→- Refactoring needed before starting next epic\n   407→- Documentation or specifications to create\n   408→\n   409→<action>Check for technical prerequisites:</action>\n   410→\n   411→- APIs or integrations that must be ready\n   412→- Data migrations or schema changes needed\n   413→- Testing infrastructure requirements\n   414→- Deployment or environment setup\n   415→\n   416→  <output>\n   417→Bob (Scrum Master): \"Alright, I've reviewed Epic {{next_epic_num}}: '{{next_epic_title}}'\"\n   418→\n   419→Alice (Product Owner): \"What are we looking at?\"\n   420→\n   421→Bob (Scrum Master): \"{{next_epic_num}} stories planned, building on the {{dependency_description}} from Epic {{epic_number}}.\"\n   422→\n   423→Charlie (Senior Dev): \"Dependencies concern me. Did we finish everything we need for that?\"\n   424→\n   425→Bob (Scrum Master): \"Good question - that's exactly what we need to explore in this retro.\"\n   426→</output>\n   427→\n   428→<action>Set {{next_epic_exists}} = true</action>\n   429→</check>\n   430→\n   431→<check if=\"next epic NOT found\">\n   432→  <output>\n   433→Bob (Scrum Master): \"Hmm, I don't see Epic {{next_epic_num}} defined yet.\"\n   434→\n   435→Alice (Product Owner): \"We might be at the end of the roadmap, or we haven't planned that far ahead yet.\"\n   436→\n   437→Bob (Scrum Master): \"No problem. We'll still do a thorough retro on Epic {{epic_number}}. The lessons will be valuable whenever we plan the next work.\"\n   438→</output>\n   439→\n   440→<action>Set {{next_epic_exists}} = false</action>\n   441→</check>\n   442→\n   443→</step>\n   444→\n   445→<step n=\"5\" goal=\"Initialize Retrospective with Rich Context\">\n   446→\n   447→<action>Load agent configurations from {agent_manifest}</action>\n   448→<action>Identify which agents participated in Epic {{epic_number}} based on story records</action>\n   449→<action>Ensure key roles present: Product Owner, Scrum Master (facilitating), Devs, Testing/QA, Architect</action>\n   450→\n   451→<output>\n   452→Bob (Scrum Master): \"Alright team, everyone's here. Let me set the stage for our retrospective.\"\n   453→\n   454→═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n   455→🔄 TEAM RETROSPECTIVE - Epic {{epic_number}}: {{epic_title}}\n   456→═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n   457→\n   458→Bob (Scrum Master): \"Here's what we accomplished together.\"\n   459→\n   460→**EPIC {{epic_number}} SUMMARY:**\n   461→\n   462→Delivery Metrics:\n   463→\n   464→- Completed: {{completed_stories}}/{{total_stories}} stories ({{completion_percentage}}%)\n   465→- Velocity: {{actual_points}} story points{{#if planned_points}} (planned: {{planned_points}}){{/if}}\n   466→- Duration: {{actual_sprints}} sprints{{#if planned_sprints}} (planned: {{planned_sprints}}){{/if}}\n   467→- Average velocity: {{points_per_sprint}} points/sprint\n   468→\n   469→Quality and Technical:\n   470→\n   471→- Blockers encountered: {{blocker_count}}\n   472→- Technical debt items: {{debt_count}}\n   473→- Test coverage: {{coverage_info}}\n   474→- Production incidents: {{incident_count}}\n   475→\n   476→Business Outcomes:\n   477→\n   478→- Goals achieved: {{goals_met}}/{{total_goals}}\n   479→- Success criteria: {{criteria_status}}\n   480→- Stakeholder feedback: {{feedback_summary}}\n   481→\n   482→Alice (Product Owner): \"Those numbers tell a good story. {{completion_percentage}}% completion is {{#if completion_percentage >= 90}}excellent{{else}}something we should discuss{{/if}}.\"\n   483→\n   484→Charlie (Senior Dev): \"I'm more interested in that technical debt number - {{debt_count}} items is {{#if debt_count > 10}}concerning{{else}}manageable{{/if}}.\"\n   485→\n   486→Dana (QA Engineer): \"{{incident_count}} production incidents - {{#if incident_count == 0}}clean epic!{{else}}we should talk about those{{/if}}.\"\n   487→\n   488→{{#if next_epic_exists}}\n   489→═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n   490→**NEXT EPIC PREVIEW:** Epic {{next_epic_num}}: {{next_epic_title}}\n   491→═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n   492→\n   493→Dependencies on Epic {{epic_number}}:\n   494→{{list_dependencies}}\n   495→\n   496→Preparation Needed:\n   497→{{list_preparation_gaps}}\n   498→\n   499→Technical Prerequisites:"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01RgbEdgdZzBzTLJjLUk89Tw","session_id":"01d3be87-3cff-45e1-920c-7390a9e4093c","uuid":"07a38c18-9519-47c2-8bc0-45be7a74e26d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T10:11:03.664Z"}
